the programme includes lectures sessions followed by discussion sessions the speakers at this camp are eminent scientists and mathematicians participants of this programme include kvpy fellows inspire scholars st year science undergraduates studying in iisc iiser's iit's niser and other central universities in the camp was hosted by two institutions iisc and iiser kolkata a total of about students attended the camp in
